%e A185700 For k=16; j=8; n=T(k-1)+j=128; 1<q|(16,8) --> {2,4,8} a(128) = c(128) - a(T(7)+4) - a(T(3)+2) - a(T(1)+1) =  810 - 8 - 1 - 1 = 800.
%e A185700   (binomial(16,8)-8*a(T(7)+4)-4*a(T(3)+2)-2*a(T(1)+1))/16 = (12870-64-4-2)/16 = 800 = a(128).
